data.description: Incredible opportunity to find this updated St Pete home that features an additional separate living space/apartment with kitchen & private bathroom that was updated in 2022 on a large corner lot.  This home features a huge yard with 2 side yards, drive space on each side and space between neighbors in the desirable Kenwood area of St Pete minutes from everything!  The entire main residence was thoughtfully renovated in 2019: BRAND NEW ROOF, APPLIANCES, HVAC, WATER HEATER, ELECTRICAL PANEL, ELECTRICAL WIRING, PLUMBING, SLIDERS, NEW WINDOWS and ATTIC INSULATION. In addition to this prime location that offers a lifestyle of riding your bike or scooter to downtown bars or some the most beautiful Florida beaches, you are also minutes from several parks and dog parks for a great outdoor lifestyle. The home is stunning with a large, modern, open kitchen with sleek dark stainless steel appliances, granite counters and a welcoming center island that is perfect for social gatherings or intimate dinners at home. The new luxury, vinyl flooring will welcome your every step throughout the home. Embrace the charming and airy atmosphere this space offers. Off the main kitchen and living area leads to a brand new bonus room or office that flows out onto the outdoor living space . Endless sunlight shines through the sliding glass doors and numerous windows throughout to enhance the overall ambiance of the home. Venture to the backyard to discover the wood deck with fenced yard that can be expanded to the side yard where you can relax in peace and seclusion while soaking in the beautiful Florida sunshine ! The spacious primary and secondary bedrooms as well as the main bath are tucked into the north side of the home for increases privacy and functionality of living. The garage improved apartment presents an additional income opportunity or a private sanctuary as an incredible master retreat for your self or guests and family members. There is also a full size laundry/storage room that is super functional. This property comes is one of the few areas of St.Petersburg that is not in a flood zone and no flood insurance is required, NO HOA or extra deed restrictions, and custom hurricane shutters are included. You'll be delighted to discover that you are just a stone's throw from the beautiful Gulf beaches , Tropicana Field, vibrant cultural hotspots, trendy eateries, scenic parks, as well as easy access to major highways. Just a few blocks from grocery stores, walking parks and so much more! Don't miss this extraordinary opportunity to keep the home as a large 3/2 residence or choose to rent out 1 side or choose to have a friend or family member live in the same home but have their own space.  Schedule your private tour today!
